      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管中国支持人民币贬值，金属价格仍下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/metals-steady-as-china-shows-support-for-under-pressure-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美元走强，中国仍表示将支持人民币，但铝价仍接近三个月低点，铁矿石价格也延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/metals-steady-as-china-shows-support-for-under-pressure-currency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:59:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行通过高于关键水平的中间价来加强人民币支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/china-maintains-grip-on-yuan-with-fix-stronger-than-7-2-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周人民币突然贬值，引发市场猜测决策者将批准人民币进一步贬值。此后，中国重申了对人民币的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/china-maintains-grip-on-yuan-with-fix-stronger-than-7-2-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东市场走强，油价维持在 10 月高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于亚洲炼油商的强劲需求，一些中东原油价格上涨，油价稳定在近三个月来的最高水平附近。]]></description>
