      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 23:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲货币跌至二十年来最低点，股市涨跌互现：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲货币对美元的汇率跌至近二十年来的最低点，股市出现波动，芯片行业蓬勃发展，但日本股市的下跌抵消了这一上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普给经济前景蒙上阴影，债券交易员认为未来一年形势严峻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/bond-traders-see-fraught-year-ahead-as-trump-shadows-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济的强劲复苏以及当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的减税和关税政策有可能使美国国债继续承压，债券交易员在进入新的一年时对前景的预期有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/bond-traders-see-fraught-year-ahead-as-trump-shadows-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
